 Description
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This is the server side code that opens a TCP connection which allows a device
to connect to the server. It is in a very rough form at the moment but is being
cpntinuously worked on.


 Planned Features
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1. Support for multiple TCP connections
2. Ability to push a new config to the device, ie poll times etc
3. Interface the server to google maps and plot the position of the vehicle



